Package com.github.mizosoft.methanol.store.redis

Interface RedisStorageExtension

All Superinterfaces:
InternalStorageExtension, StorageExtension
public interface RedisStorageExtension extends InternalStorageExtension
A StorageExtension that provides storage on either a Redis Standalone instance or a Redis Cluster. Instances are created with RedisStorageExtension.Builder.
